name: G New Doc
body:
G New Doc
===

A google chrome extension to create new Google Doc with only two clicks.

Avaliable document types:

* Document
* Presentation
* Spreadsheet
* Form
* Drawing
* Table

Install
---

Install from [Chrome Web Store](https://chrome.google.com/extensions/detail/ebmobgdemdgppppmboipgkdfagfnleaj)
